  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Scales for Repetitive and Restricted Behaviors in Children, Adolescents, and Adults With Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study to Evaluate and Explore Scales for Repetitive and Restricted Behaviors and Digital Biomarkers in Children, Adolescents, and Adults With Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD)</official_title>
