  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a non-drug study seeking to characterize different scales to measure repetitive and
      restrictive behaviors in different ASD sub-populations over time. This study will also
      explore the use of digital biomarkers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
